Manual Override flag per ADR-036 + ADR-048. When set to Yes, Flow 1's CP BU inheritance logic skips the write entirely and preserves whatever pei_owningbu is on the record (admin's manual choice). When No (default), Flow 1 derives Owning BU from the Parent BP's classification per ADR-040 / ADR-051. Used for the rare CP that needs ownership different from its Parent BP's classification (e.g., a CP under a Horizontal BP that legitimately belongs to a specific BU's audit scope).
